sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as app-admin / app-api-ts
    participant Connectors as app-connectors
    participant Vendor as Fournisseur OAuth
    participant Store as Secret store + runtime snapshot

    Admin->>Connectors: creer ou mettre a jour la connexion
    Admin->>Connectors: authorize/start
    Connectors->>Store: creer authorizationSession
    Connectors-->>Admin: authorizationUrl + state + expiresAt
    Admin->>Vendor: redirection utilisateur
    Vendor-->>Admin: callback avec code + state
    Admin->>Connectors: authorize/complete
    Connectors->>Store: relire authorizationSession
    Connectors->>Vendor: echange code -> token
    Vendor-->>Connectors: access/refresh token
    Connectors->>Store: sceller credentials + mettre a jour snapshot
    Connectors-->>Admin: connexion autorisee
